CAM@ C43014 Nissan Cedric 130 Special Six (Mk 2) 1969 All Japan Stocker Fuji 300km Series Winner S. Suzuki

Purchased: 2014

There were 2 races in the 1969 All Japan Stocker Fuji 300km Series. Since the winner of the first race of the 1969 series looks like this I will assume this is the car from the second race of the 1969 series. Click here for a group shot of all 4 racing Cedrics from CAM@.
